<br><b><font size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#4681BD" weight="bold">.:Dazed and confused:.</font></b><br>
<small><font size="1" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#0F7B66">Tuesday, March 11 2003</font></small><br><br>

<font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><font color="#FFFFFF">I feel really dazed lately, and Im not sure why.... its not good. But spring break is coming up so that might solve some things right?</P><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY>
Weapons, Strategy and War coming up.... </p></font></font>
