<br><b><font size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#4681BD" weight="bold">.:What if...:.</font></b><br>
<small><font size="1" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#0F7B66">Monday, March 10 2003</font></small><br><br>

<font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><font color="#FFFFFF">What if there really is no model for priced online music sharing that is acceptable to the public and profitable for the corporations?</P><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY>
What if there is no life on other planets?</P><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY>
What if there will never be a cure for cancer?</P><P ALIGN=JUSTIFY>
Just more random thoughts about things we always figured would happen, but what if they don't or can't happen?</p></font></font>
